WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Film from a steady position — down-the-line or face-on.

2
00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Keep the whole body in frame.

3
00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Upload the clip on the Video Analysis screen.

4
00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
SwingVantage breaks the swing into phases and looks for common faults in each.

5
00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Every finding comes with a plain-language explanation and how strongly we believe it — shown as a confidence level.

6
00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:24.000
Visual conclusions are labeled as estimates, not measurements.

7
00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:28.000
Use them as a smart starting point, not the final word.
